因\r\n疫情而遲誤不變期間，得向法院聲請回復原狀。\r\n                              書記官  楊雅媖\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　10　　月　　18　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDM/110%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c161%2c20211015%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDM,110,簡,161,20211015,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"161","JDATE":"20211015","JTITLE":"妨害自由"}